rong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>I added <strong>indexes</strong> in plugin database tables, so the queries run much faster than before</li>\n<li>now you have the opportunity to <strong>archive</strong> (=delete) the detailed report of old newsletters and keep only the aggregate info: it make plugin operations faster</li>\n<li>you can use also <strong>themes</strong> based on a <strong>php</strong> file, not only html (thanks to eqhes!)</li>\n<li>now there is an option to publish or not newsletters online (see in <em>Newsletter → Settings → tab General</em>)<br />\n(Here you are the full <a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/alo-easymail/changelog/" title="plugin changelog on WP.org" target="_blank">changelog</a>).<br />\nYou can go on WP.org and <a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/alo-easymail/" target="_blank">download it</a>.<br />\nThe upgrade will alter plugin database tables, so: <strong>after upgrade files always remember to de-activate and activate it again!</strong></p>\n<p>You can read guide, faqs&#8230; (see links in right sidebar) and use the <a href="http://www.eventualo.net/forum/">forum</a> to share your feedback. And <strong>you can contribute</strong> to keep the plugin update donating some money to me. </p>\n<form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post">\n<input name="cmd" type="hidden" value="_s-xclick" />\n<input name="lc" type="hidden" value="EN" />\n<input name="hosted_button_id" type="hidden" value="9E6BPXEZVQYHA" />\n<input style="border: 0pt none;" alt="PayPal" name="submit" src="https://www.paypal.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donate_SM.gif" type="image" /> <img src="https://www.paypal.com/it_IT/i/scr/pixel.gif" border="0" alt="" width="1" height="1" /><br />\n</form>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:56:"http://www.eventualo.net/blog/2011/10/easymail-2-3/feed/";s:7:"a